{"type":"message","id":"67c1ecee","parentId":"e9a497e2","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:35:46.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No memory files exist yet - this is a fresh workspace. Just BOOTSTRAP.md exists which I already read. Let me greet HALEI and ask what they want to do.\n\nSince this is a fresh workspace (March 2026), and BOOTSTRAP.md exists, the system prompt says I should introduce myself and figure out who I am together with the user. But since SOUL.md already defines my persona as a TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品专家, I should embody that persona.\n\nLet me greet HALEI in Chinese since that's the configured language and context."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好 HALEI！我是你的选品专家 🤝\n\n今天想做什么？比如：\n- 查看/管理飞书多维表格数据\n- 开始一次选品采集流程\n- 或者其他 TikTok Shop 发饰相关的事情"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775720138808,"responseId":"062689cb6b3c8799638b9169e6bd912d"}}
