{"type":"message","id":"c68a0154","parentId":"7925d438","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:35:49.475Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b524122b9c0e4c4f743432067a22\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-09 15:35 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b524122b9c0e4c4f743432067a22]\nou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 你能使用vibesurf skill开的 www.baidu.com"}],"timestamp":1775720149470}}
